NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|I do have a question as to whether 1D is forcing by a passed hand. You can play it either way. I like to play new suits still forcing, but it is reasonable, and probably more common, to play them as non-forcing. So, because Boater passed originally, some people feel that 1D should not be forcing.|
