PG| ***** 115 ***** |


AT|

{  A hand rich in aces should be upgraded, even if those aces are unsupported.  }|
PG| ***** 116 ***** |


AT|

{  Honors in partner's short suit(s) are usually not worth much.  }|
PG| ***** 117 ***** |


